[normal]1.3
[normal]              
[normal]              
[normal]ScotPHN
[normal] is 
[normal]hosted by NHS Health 
[normal]Scotland;
[normal] it is 
[normal]open to everyone in Scotland who has a professional interest and 
[normal]significant involvement in the wider health improvement agenda including staff from the NHS, local authorities, academia and others.
[normal]  The aims of ScotPHN are:
[normal]•
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]To undertake prioritised national pieces of work where there is a clearly identified need.
[normal]•
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]To fac
[normal]ilitate information exchange between public health practitioners, link with other networks and share learning.
[normal] 
[normal]•
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]To create effective communication amongst professionals and the public to allow efficient co-ordination of public health activity.
[normal] 
[normal]•
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]To support a
[normal]nd enhance the capabilities and functionality of the Scottish Directors of Public Health Group.
